         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">27/2/82. ¶  ¶ I feel, sure, dear Sir Joseph, that the experiment initiated by me to send living plants from K.G. Sound ¶  to Kew in close cases during the cool season will result in manyfold successes...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.02.27</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1882-90, f. 4.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">27/2/82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I feel, sure, dear Sir Joseph, that the experiment initiated by me to send living plants from K.G. Sound<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">King George Sound, WA.</p>
               </note> to Kew in close cases during the cool season will result in manyfold successes.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See, for example, M to J. Hooker, 26 August 1881.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will be gratified to hear that I have secured the Sonderian collections by purchase on behalf of the Victorian Government.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">You will ... collections <seg style="font-style: italic; ">is marked with a line in the margin</seg>. For M's requests, and the Government's final agreement to purchase the collection, see M to J. Moore, 3 October 1863; M to J. McCulloch, 25 September 1866 (in this edition as 66-09-25a); M to C. Duffy, 20 September 1871; and M to L. Smith, 16 February 1882 and notes to that letter.</p>
               </note> I bought the <name key="Glumaceae">Glumaceae</name> many years ago already;<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to J. MacPherson, 6 April 1870.</p>
               </note> but one great gem of the collection, as you know, the South African plants, went to Stockholm.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See Nordenstam (1980).</p>
               </note> My negotiations with my poor departed friend concerning his collections commenced more than 20 years ago.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Glumaceae">Glumaceae</name>
            </p>
         </div>
